## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

GlobalPath University Admissions Assistant is a frontend-based web application designed to guide prospective students through the admission process.  

The system provides automated support features such as program matching, scholarship eligibility checking, application tracking simulation, and a rule-based chatbot.

This project demonstrates how digital automation can improve student experience and reduce administrative workload.

---

## ğŸ¯ Objectives

- Provide 24/7 automated admission guidance
- Help students select suitable programs
- Check scholarship eligibility instantly
- Simulate application tracking
- Reduce repetitive queries handled by counselors
- Improve enrollment engagement

